Cell["\<\
These molecular orbitals and their relative energies are shown in Figure \
11.7. The MOs depicted were calculated at a higher level of theory \
(Hartree-Fock vs. H\[UDoubleDot]ckel), but they display the same general \
features predicted by the H\[UDoubleDot]ckel wavefunctions.\
\>", "Text",
